65f5201a-9c62-4e74-95a0-4f8ac2f9a920.title: <player>
65f5201a-9c62-4e74-95a0-4f8ac2f9a920.text: Brother Omad needs the wine for the party.

647bcd0d-d711-427e-aeb1-4da47178e271.title: Brother Cedric
647bcd0d-d711-427e-aeb1-4da47178e271.text: Oh dear, oh dear, I knew I had to do something!

f90acb2a-f085-4d4b-8fb6-b1576d6e3879.title: Brother Cedric
f90acb2a-f085-4d4b-8fb6-b1576d6e3879.text:
Pleashhh, find me a jug of water. Once I'm sober I'll
'elp you take the wine back.

74d7f848-e9f8-4dfa-be14-d786599d98fc.title: Note
74d7f848-e9f8-4dfa-be14-d786599d98fc.text: What happens if you already have water?

17f783cb-01f3-4995-9900-abeb2ede69b7.title: Brother Cedric
17f783cb-01f3-4995-9900-abeb2ede69b7.text: Hic up! Oh my head! I need a jug of water.

75fb0cf6-5ad9-477f-856b-47671ef50b4a.title: <player>
75fb0cf6-5ad9-477f-856b-47671ef50b4a.text: Cedric! Here, drink! I have some water.

ce675475-b9ee-454e-aab9-eacebaa47a5a.text: You hand the monk a jug of water.

6ff2c534-0380-4409-9469-79b87b09306d.title: Brother Cedric
6ff2c534-0380-4409-9469-79b87b09306d.text: Now I just need to fix this cart and we can go party.

options.text: No, I've helped enough monks today!
遰 Yes, I'd be happy to!

7c336994-e29c-4a35-b42e-72a8ee7b1bde.title: <player>
7c336994-e29c-4a35-b42e-72a8ee7b1bde.text: No, I've helped enough monks today!

80894a22-ecb1-4eb5-9b57-36f53e080ffe.title: Brother Cedric
80894a22-ecb1-4eb5-9b57-36f53e080ffe.text:
In that case I'd better drink more wine! It helps me
think.

736b9c9b-eb4b-4907-bf2f-80189a7d125d.title: Brother Cedric
736b9c9b-eb4b-4907-bf2f-80189a7d125d.text:
Excellent, I just need some wood. Some plain logs, or
maybe a basic plank.

4e7a70d6-08b0-42ea-a116-23d5fa36f50d.title: <player>
4e7a70d6-08b0-42ea-a116-23d5fa36f50d.text: OK, I'll see what I can find.

a5105616-4db0-4339-9c5e-a4e7684a1d4e.title: <player>
a5105616-4db0-4339-9c5e-a4e7684a1d4e.text: I'll see if I can get some.

01007d73-49f2-4e04-89e4-dfbfb90cd478.title: Brother Cedric
01007d73-49f2-4e04-89e4-dfbfb90cd478.text: Did you manage to get some wood?

87bd0512-df1c-4e8d-b6c5-0577b71aee71.title: Brother Cedric
87bd0512-df1c-4e8d-b6c5-0577b71aee71.text:
Well done! Now I'll fix this cart. You head back to
Brother Omad and tell him I'll be there soon.

f7cee6d3-6605-4b64-939c-5366b06ac861.text: You show Cedric a wooden plank.

5cc94453-e925-4709-af55-7f07baa026d6.title: Brother Cedric
5cc94453-e925-4709-af55-7f07baa026d6.text:
Hi, I'm almost done here. Could you tell Omad that I'll
be back soon?

f1f002e8-d715-4ec9-bb81-17f5610f3e92.title: Brother Cedric
f1f002e8-d715-4ec9-bb81-17f5610f3e92.text:
Brother Omad sends you his thanks! He won't be in a
fit state to thank you in person.
